data.description: INCREDIBLE VALUE! A spacious 4 bed, 4 bath, 2 car in DESIRABLE Sendera Ranch. This versatile floorplan boasts EXCEPTIONAL curb appeal and MODERN INTERIOR FINISHES, including dramatic gray walls, sleek, white SUBWAY TILES and bright, natural, wood-look tile flooring. The eat-in kitchen features built-in gas burners, all stainless appliances and an abundance of flawless SHAKER STYLE CABINETRY, all open to the living room, complete with cozy fireplace and soaring ceilings. The thoughtfully designed floorplan separates the primary bedroom from all other rooms in the home, provides informal and formal dining spaces as well as a bonus-family room upstairs with its own bathroom. This like-new home is located in the award winning Northwest ISD school district just minutes away from Alliance and Presidio shopping. Additional amenities include multiple community pools, splash park, playgrounds, tennis courts & biking trails. Come see why Haslet, TX is quickly becoming THE place to call home!
